quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  6,11,"Say: \"Walk/move in the Earth/land, then look/wonder about how was the liars`/falsifiers` end/turn (result)"
  6,12,"Say: \"To whom, what (is) in the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth?\" Say: \"To God, He decreed on Himself the mercy, He will gather/collect you to the Resurrection Day, no doubt/suspicion in it, those who lost themselves, so they are not believing"
  6,13,"And for Him (is) what settled in the night and the daytime, and He (is) the hearing/listening, the knowledgeable"
  6,14,"Say: \"Is other than God, I take (as) a guardian , (the) creator (of) the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth, and He feeds and is not fed.\" Say: \"I was ordered/commanded that I be first (of) who surrendered/submitted, and do not be (E) from the sharers/takers of partners (with God)"
  6,15,"Say: \"That I, I fear if I disobeyed my Lord (from) a great day`s torture"
  6,16,"Who is diverted from it (on) that day, so He had mercy upon him, and that (is) the clear/evident success/triumph"
  6,17,"And if God touches you with harm, so (there is)no remover/uncoverer for it except He, and if He touches you with goodness , so He is on every thing capable"
  6,18,"And He is the defeater/conqueror over His worshippers/slaves, and He is the wise/judicious, the expert/experienced"
  6,19,"Say: \"Which thing (is) greater (in) testimony/certification ?\" Say: \"God (is an) honest witness between me and between you (P), and (it is) transmitted/revealed to me this the Koran, to warn you with it and who (was) reached (informed); that you are witnessing/testifying (E), that with God, (are) other Gods.\" Say: \"I do not witness/testify.\" Say: \"But He is one God, and that I am innocent from what you share (with God)"
  6,20,"Those whom We brought to (gave) them The Book , they know it as they know their sons, those who lost themselves, so they do not believe"